pageProduct.name: Autili Kids Liquid Calcium + Vitamin D3 60 Softgel Capsules
pageProduct.description:
Warnings

Keep out of reach of children. This product is taken as assistance if dietary intake is inadequate. Do bot take with similar calcium and vitamin D products is case exceeding recommended daily dose.

Common Uses

Vitamin D and Calcium are important nutrients for supporting healthy bones and teeth. Calcium is basic components of the bone and teeth. Vitamin D helps the absorption of calcium.

Directions

(One year old: pierce & squeeze into food/drink. 2-4 yrs.: chew with adults supervision) Under 1yr, ½ capsule; 4 yrs., 1 capsule; above 4 yrs. and adults, 1-2 capsules per day. Take after a meal or as directed by your healthcare professional.
